## Terminal goal — RIBOZYME row in 16-cell matrix

RIBOZYME 은 4 disease class 각각 catalytic RNA design. Meta `.roadmap.hexa_bio` §0 의 **R 행**.

| Cell  | Disease       | 후보 ribozyme (예)                                       |
|-------|---------------|-----------------------------------------------------------|
| R·α   | AML           | FLT3-ITD 또는 NPM1c mutant mRNA cleavage                 |
| R·β   | SCD           | β-globin precursor trans-splicing 교정                    |
| R·γ   | pan-cov       | conserved viral RNA region cleavage                       |
| R·δ   | senolytic     | SASP key mRNA (예: IL-6) cleavage                        |

**Cell DoD**: in-silico ribozyme design + k_cat/K_M Eigen-Hammes ceiling margin + 12-nt catalytic core + 4-state reaction ladder + witness → `state/discovery_absorption/registry.jsonl`.

