## Require (verb-specific)

- **(R-R1)** Ribozyme output schema = RNA spec (sequence + 2D/3D structure + predicted k_cat/K_M + 4-state ladder)
- **(R-R2)** Sister-axis 분담 (C0a 결과 2026-05-05 — F-RB-5 **PASS WITH MITIGATION**): hexa-bio RIBOZYME = catalytic-RNA **architectural primitive** (active-site σ(6)=12 core residues, τ(6)=4 reaction states, k_cat/K_M Eigen-Hammes diffusion ceiling, in-silico chemical-kinetics simulation L0-L4); `life/crispr-gene-editing/` = Cas9-sgRNA **system integration** + clinical delivery (downstream, no genus collision); `life/synbio/` = **in-vitro selection / SELEX** library construction + metabolic-chassis embedding — handshake point: SELEX 가 ribozyme discovery 의 selection 단계 owner (RIBOZYME design 단계와 명확 분리, L9 application 으로 routing).
- **(R-R3)** Meta `.roadmap.hexa_bio` §E (R1-R8) 전 도메인 Require 상속

