- **[UNDEFINED] F-RB-1 / F-RB-3 sub-falsifiers (lines 64, 68)** — deadline / 본문 / interim checkpoint 부재 (open-ended). **Resolution:** 정식 등록 또는 abandon 결정.
  **Draft 2026-05-06:** Mirror NANOBOT F-NB-1/F-NB-3 pattern (3
  measurable axes per claim, all with 2026-09-28 interim deadline):
  - **F-RB-1-genus** — RIBOZYME genus separates from WEAVE (DNA
